{"id": "art-199", "label": "Art. 199", "title": "Art. 199", "slug": "art-199", "content": "<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:4.0pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><b style='mso-bidi-font-weight:normal'><span style='color:\nblack'>Art. 199 </span></b></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_936128721\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1952\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_936128721\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(1)<span class=SpellE>Dispozi&#355;iile</span> art. </span><span\nstyle='color:#1B1B1B'>160 alin. (1)</span><span style='color:black'>, alin. (1<sup>2</sup>)\n<span class=SpellE>&#351;i</span> alin. (2), precum <span class=SpellE>&#351;i</span>\nale art. 160<sup>1</sup> se aplic&#259; în mod corespunz&#259;tor.</span><br\nstyle='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![if !supportLineBreakNewLine]><br style='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![endif]></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_2026909072\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1951\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_2026909072\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(2)La <span class=SpellE>societ&#259;&#355;ile</span> care\nnu se încadreaz&#259; în prevederile art. 160 alin. (1), adunarea <span\nclass=SpellE>asocia&#355;ilor</span> poate numi unul sau mai <span\nclass=SpellE>mul&#355;i</span> cenzori ori un auditor financiar.</span><br\nstyle='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![if !supportLineBreakNewLine]><br style='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![endif]></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='color:black'>(3)Dac&#259; num&#259;rul <span\nclass=SpellE>asocia&#355;ilor</span> trece de 15, numirea cenzorilor este\nobligatorie.</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='color:black'>(4)<span class=SpellE>Dispozi&#355;iile</span>\nprev&#259;zute pentru cenzorii <span class=SpellE>societ&#259;&#355;ilor</span>\npe <span class=SpellE>ac&#355;iuni</span> se aplic&#259; <span class=SpellE>&#351;i</span>\ncenzorilor din <span class=SpellE>societ&#259;&#355;ile</span> cu\nr&#259;spundere limitat&#259;.</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1652652653\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1950\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1652652653\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(5)În lips&#259; de cenzori sau, dup&#259; caz, de auditor\nfinanciar, fiecare dintre <span class=SpellE>asocia&#355;i</span>, care nu este\nadministrator al <span class=SpellE>societ&#259;&#355;ii</span>, va exercita\ndreptul de control pe care <span class=SpellE>asocia&#355;ii</span> îl au în <span\nclass=SpellE>societ&#259;&#355;ile</span> în nume colectiv.</span><br\nstyle='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![if !supportLineBreakNewLine]><br style='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![endif]></p>"}